      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "白盔白甲白旗号，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00002",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、关兴、张苞引刘备同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00003",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "二弟呀，三弟呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00004",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "回龙",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "孤的好兄弟！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00005",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "孤王心恸哭嚎啕。决意兴兵把仇报，扫平了东吴恨方消。请过了灵牌王怀抱，",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00006",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关兴取灵牌，跪。刘备坐，接灵牌。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00007",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反西皮二六",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "点点珠泪往下抛。当年桃园结义好，胜似那骨肉亲同胞。不幸今朝分别了，眼望黄泉去路遥。徐州遭离乱，愚兄我暂栖河北投袁绍，你身在曹营念故交。上马金，下马银，富贵你不要，挂印封金辞奸曹。匹马单刀保皇嫂，过五关斩六将，擂鼓三通把蔡阳的首级枭，可算得盖世的英豪！恼恨东吴行奸巧，害孤的二弟归天曹。此仇此恨怎能够不报，怎能不报！",
      "text_length": 157
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00008",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "二弟呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00009",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关兴起，接灵牌。刘备起。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00010",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "踏平东吴恨方消！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00011",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "伯父！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00012",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "伯父不必痛哀悼，珍重天年春秋高。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00013",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "非是为伯珠泪掉，孤与尔父生死交。哭罢了二弟把三弟叫，",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00014",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "翼德啊，三弟啊！啊！难得见的好兄弟啊！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00015",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张苞取灵牌，跪。刘备坐，接灵牌。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00016",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反西皮二六",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "哭声三弟泪洒在白袍。当年同把董卓讨，弟兄们阵前显英豪。虎牢关曾把吕布的发冠挑，长坂坡前喝断了当阳桥。夜战马超胆气豪，义收严颜颇有略韬。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00017",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "快西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "恼恨那范疆张达两个贼强盗，害孤三弟，二贼脱逃。如今犯人俱解到，纵然我手刃狂徒难把恨消。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00018",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张苞接灵牌，起。刘备起。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00019",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "快西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "越思越想心头恼，这血海深仇，",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00020",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "东吴是根苗。今日兴兵把仇报，不杀孙权不还朝。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00021",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "一片忠诚天可表，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000008_e00022",
      "play_id": "80000008",
      "scene_id": "80000008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘备接灵牌。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
